TestClassMooseWithHistory README 

??A future MadMongers presentation???

The object is to test Test::Class::Moose:History with an old T:C:M project

1 Read 'Install.TCMH.txt' on how I installed T:C:M:H on a Ubuntu 18.04
2 View Ovid's post 'Saving your test suite history'
    review $ t/tcm.t :: --report
3 I could not get 
       my $report = Test::Class::Moose::History::Report->new;
       my $failures = $report->last_failures;
    to work!
4 Did not know to how code
       $ prove t/tcm.t :: --failures
    Is it last_failures and/or top_failures
5 Created a new argument for t/tcm.t, '--tc', for test_classes argument
    for T:C:M:Runner
6 Look at 'prove_it.sh'
7 If t/tcm.t is not run with   :: --report   it will not put any
    history into the database

